Preheat oven to 250 degrees F. Remove crusts from bread with a serrated edge or an electric knife. Cut slices in half. Stir together butter, SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, and orange peel. Spread butter mixture thinly onto each side of bread. Arrange in a single layer on a baking sheet. Bake for 40 minutes or until dry and crisp, turning after 20 minutes. Transfer to wire racks to cool. Store in an air-tight tin.